Eggplant Parmesan

Eggplant Parmesan

Ingredients

  1. Eggplant
  2. Breadcrumbs (Panko)
  3. 1 Egg Yolk
  4. Pasta sauce
  5. Shredded Cheese

Instructions

  1. Dip the eggplant pieces in the egg yolk and cover with breadcrumbs
  2. Dollop pasta sauce on a aluminum bedpan and drop in the covered eggplant pieces
  3. Cover the top of the eggplants with pasta sauce and add cheese
  4. Bake at 375F for 30 min
